      <title>香港财经事务局局长谈香港资本市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/hk-secretary-for-financial-services-on-hk-capital-market-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港财经事务及库务局局长许志永讨论了政府如何看待香港的传统企业。他在亚洲金融论坛的间隙与 David Ingles 和 Rebecca Choong Wilkins 进行了交谈，主题是“与 Haslinda Amin 的见解”。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-13/hk-secretary-for-financial-services-on-hk-capital-market-video</guid>
