    <item>
      <title>雷恩称无论美联储采取何种举措，欧洲央行都需要进一步降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/more-ecb-rate-cuts-needed-irrespective-of-fed-moves-rehn-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会成员奥利·雷恩表示，无论美联储采取何种措施，欧洲央行都应继续降低借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/more-ecb-rate-cuts-needed-irrespective-of-fed-moves-rehn-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 07:33:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
