    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元上涨、油价飙升，卢比跌破 86 创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/rupee-falls-past-86-to-new-record-on-dollar-rally-oil-surge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国强劲的就业数据抑制了对美联储进一步降息的预期，且油价飙升影响了印度这个石油净进口国的信心，印度卢比兑美元跌破了86的关键心理水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-13/rupee-falls-past-86-to-new-record-on-dollar-rally-oil-surge</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 04:57:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国对俄罗斯制裁引发混乱，油价创四个月新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国对俄罗斯能源行业实施新一轮制裁，威胁到石油供应，导致亚洲主要进口国感到困惑，油价上涨至四个多月来的最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-13</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jan 2025 23:02:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储利率前景导致股市下跌，英镑下跌：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/asian-stocks-under-pressure-after-blowout-us-jobs-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五非农就业数据公布后，交易员削减对美联储降息的押注，亚洲股市随欧洲和美国股指期货下跌。英镑延续上周的跌势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-12/asian-stocks-under-pressure-after-blowout-us-jobs-markets-wrap</guid>
